{
  "stem": "18778.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 209.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I felt so badly for them, because they couldn't touch their father's hand or hug him or-- they just could kind of shout at each other, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was down there in this little boat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- they would be either on deck or in their porthole trying to holler back at him, and so was everybody else doing that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then all kinds of entrepreneurs came out, kids that would dive for pennies and-- or they would sell oranges or pineapples for pennies and throw them up on deck with a little bag attached to the fruit.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then you'd put your little bit of money in there and then throw it back down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a circus all day long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And eventually there were negotiations going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The committee which had been formed by the captain of course was in session 24 hours a day by this time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father was chosen as chairman of this committee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The initial committee were five gentlemen and eventually two others joined.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Most of them were doctors and lawyers, and I think there were two businessmen on the committee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were sitting with the captains sending out telegrams to New York, to the Jewish agencies, because the Cuban government decided they would ask for an additional $500 per head and then they would consider perhaps letting us off and perhaps putting us in some kind of a-- a camp somewhere in Cuba.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And somebody came from New York and had the money with him, but argued about the amount with the-- with the president of Cuba.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this argument did not turn out in a favorable way.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
